@@TJvCustomAppXMLStorage
Summary
  This is the ancestor for all XML storage backend
Description
  This component provides the basis for an in memory XML storage backend. Derive a class from this one
  and implement the virtual methods to store the in memory XML file in the appropriate media (file,
  database...)

